t: "When you see them, their appearance impresses you. And when they speak, you listen to their Ë¹impressiveËº speech. But they are Ë¹justËº like Ë¹worthlessËº planks of wood leaned Ë¹against a wallËº. They think every cry is against them. They are the enemy, so beware of them. May God condemn them! How can they be deluded Ë¹from the truthËº"